to be handled.

255
00:20:04,412 --> 00:20:05,744
In three weeks he'll be...

256
00:20:05,830 --> 00:20:07,287
Yes. He'll be melted.

257
00:20:10,042 --> 00:20:11,042
Unless...

258
00:20:15,256 --> 00:20:16,337
In your basement.

259
00:20:18,718 --> 00:20:20,129
