260
00:20:21,262 --> 00:20:23,254
How badly do you want this, Jess?

261
00:20:30,646 --> 00:20:31,853
[water trickling]

262
00:20:56,672 --> 00:20:58,254
Oh, God.

263
00:21:02,136 --> 00:21:05,675
Jess, give me a hand. You gotta
give me a hand here, Jess.

264
00:21:06,724 --> 00:21:08,181
Try to free the arm.

265
00:21:08,267 --> 00:21:10,224
Get the arm off
the banister there.

266
00:21:13,689 --> 00:21:16,056
Jesse, for God's sake,
I'm losing him!

267
00:21:25,618 --> 00:21:27,450
- [doorbell rings]
- [Jessica whimpers]

268
00:21:28,662 --> 00:21:30,198
[grunting]

269
