275
00:21:59,193 --> 00:22:01,526
[sighs] I came all this way.

276
00:22:01,612 --> 00:22:03,812
- I'm gonna have to charge you for my time.
- [thumping]

277
00:22:05,950 --> 00:22:07,407
Will you be wanting me tomorrow?

278
00:22:08,285 --> 00:22:10,151
No. Uh...

279
00:22:10,955 --> 00:22:13,868
Actually, I have decided
to take your advice.

280
00:22:13,958 --> 00:22:16,792
I-I'm... I'm putting Mr. Valdemar
into a hospital.

281
00:22:17,378 --> 00:22:20,371
- I won't be needing you anymore.
- Well, it is about time.

282
00:22:20,464 --> 00:22:22,171
A man in his advanced state.

283
00:22:22,842 --> 00:22:25,505
I'm here. I would be happy
to look in on him.

284
00:22:25,594 --> 00:22:28,257
[Jessica] Uh, no. Uh, the doctor's
with him right now.

285
00:22:28,347 --> 00:22:30,930
Well, I'm sorry to lose the work,

286
00:22:31,016 --> 00:22:34,384
