379
00:32:08,969 --> 00:32:10,505
Uh, Valdemar?

380
00:32:14,099 --> 00:32:15,465
Are you there?

381
00:32:16,643 --> 00:32:19,056
[Ernest] Yes.

382
00:32:26,945 --> 00:32:31,531
Valdemar, uh,
are you still, uh...

383
00:32:31,616 --> 00:32:33,699
[Ernest] Sleeping.

384
00:32:35,370 --> 00:32:36,486
Sleeping?

385
00:32:36,997 --> 00:32:38,579
[Ernest] Yes.

386
00:32:39,458 --> 00:32:41,370
No.

387
00:32:41,460 --> 00:32:44,999
I have been sleeping,

388
00:32:45,964 --> 00:32:47,580
and now...

