390
00:32:51,678 --> 00:32:54,216
Oh, Mother of God.

391
00:32:58,935 --> 00:33:00,096
[Robert] Valdemar.

392
00:33:07,611 --> 00:33:08,727
Valdemar.

393
00:33:12,657 --> 00:33:14,239
Valdemar, can you hear me?

394
00:33:23,001 --> 00:33:24,993
[footsteps approaching]

