400
00:33:45,398 --> 00:33:48,562
I don't know. I mean,
I don't know what's going on here.

401
00:33:49,152 --> 00:33:52,987
All I can think is that he was
hypnotized when he died, so...

402
00:33:53,073 --> 00:33:56,237
