466
00:38:17,295 --> 00:38:20,003
many others.

467
00:38:20,965 --> 00:38:22,922
Looking at me.

468
00:38:23,718 --> 00:38:25,425
Watching me.

469
00:38:26,554 --> 00:38:29,262
They want something.

470
00:38:31,142 --> 00:38:32,849
These, uh, others...

471
00:38:33,394 --> 00:38:34,805
can you see them?

472
00:38:35,396 --> 00:38:38,935
